<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(هـ ز ز)</span> : هَزَزْتُهُ هَزَّا مِنْ بَابِ قَتَلَ حَرَّكْتُهُ فَاهْتَزَّ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَالْهَزَاهِزُ الْفِتَنُ يَهْتَزُّ فِيهَا النَّاسُ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>